These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, pakistani, polish, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: fish, goat, cat, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the french##1
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the polish##3
4. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
5. the malaysian is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
6. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
7. the pakistani is somewhere between the french and the owner of the goat##7
8. the pakistani and the owner of the hedgehog have the same parity positions##9
9. the polish and the owner of the fish have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | french | pakistani | polish     | malaysian |
| Pet           | cat   | hedgehog     | goat | fish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, writing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is fishing and the person drinking mirinda have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##8
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
6. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate     | soy-milk    | 7up | mirinda    |
| Hobby      | filmmaking | hiking | writing      | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, almond-milk, water
There 4 different types of food: pear, pepper, radish, kale
1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person eating radish##5
2. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating pear##1
7. the person eating pear is not to the left of the person eating pepper##8
8. the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating pepper have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | almond-milk   | lemonade    | water  |
| Food       | pepper | kale | pear | radish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, librarian, freelancer, nurse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, ambient, pop, soul
1. the fan disco is the librarian##1
2. the fan ambient is on the right of the fan pop##1
3. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
4. the fan soul is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
5. the fan ambient is on the left of the electrician##1
6. the nurse and the fan soul have the same parity positions##9
7. the freelancer is on the left or right of the electrician##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | nurse | freelancer | electrician  | librarian |
| Music-Genre   | pop             | ambient          | soul | disco    |

