.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, metal, jazz, electronic
4 different pets are kept: frog, bird, hamster, horse
1. the fan jazz is not the owner of the hamster##6
2. the owner of the frog and the fan indie have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the bird and the fan metal have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the fan jazz##5
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the fan electronic##1
6. the fan metal is not the owner of the bird##6
7. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan metal##5
8. the owner of the frog is on the right of the fan indie##1
9. the owner of the horse is not the fan electronic##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | indie | jazz | electronic  | metal |
| Pet           | bird   | frog     | hamster | horse      |

