4. the chinese and the person watching martial-arts movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching sports movies and the chinese have different parity positions##9
6. the spanish is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
7. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
8. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the colombian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
