.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, onion, mango, tomato
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, skateboard, bus, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person eating nectarine##8
2. the person eating tomato and the person driving the scooter have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
5. the person eating onion is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the scooter##7
6. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
