.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, kale, pineapple, pear
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, nigerian, french, brazilian
1. the person eating pear is not the brazilian##6
2. the brazilian is not to the right of the dutch##8
3. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person eating pear##8
4. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
5. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the french##3
6. the brazilian is on the far left##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
8. the person eating cucumber is the nigerian##1
9. the person eating pear and the dutch have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | kale   | pear    | pineapple | cucumber    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | dutch | french   | nigerian |

