4. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
8. the person watching martial-arts movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching musical movies and the person drinking juice have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
