.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, tea, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, salsa, house, reggae
 1. the person drinking coffee and the fan house have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 3. the fan folk is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking sprite##7
 4. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan house is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk and the fan salsa have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the fan reggae##3
 9. the fan reggae is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the fan folk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | soy-milk | tea  | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | house     | folk | salsa     |

