.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, card-games, skydiving, cooking
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 6. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
 7. the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is card-games have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 9. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is card-games have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk        | sprite   | fanta      |
| Hobby      | cooking | skydiving | card-games | photography |

 